<sections> 
  <clause id="_management_oversight_of_information_security" inline-header="false" obligation="normative"><title>Management oversight of information security</title><clause id="_general" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">   
  <title>General</title>   
  <requirement id="_ae06acc4-e378-4a5d-99ef-2f580289abc0"><label>/ss/584/2015/general/632</label><subject>The Cloud Service Provider’s management and board of directors</subject><description><p id="_c44cdb07-af17-4173-b34a-7dec504b1fca">The Cloud Service Provider’s management and board of directors shall be responsible for the following requirements and audit procedures.</p>    
</description><specification exclude="true">     
  <p id="_4f55a607-00a1-4e72-8d93-bb9c1d602607">be responsible for the following requirements and audit procedures</p>     
</specification></requirement>   
</clause>  
<clause id="_level_1_requirements_and_audit_procedures" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">   
  <title>Level 1 requirements and audit procedures</title>   
  <requirement id="_b544297c-ca71-46d1-ab7e-1c319e583b32"><label>/ss/584/2015/level/1</label><subject>The Cloud Service Provider’s management and board of directors</subject><specification exclude="false">     
  <ol id="_935f097a-ad64-4b1f-b508-811ec8fbf25e" type="arabic">      
  <li>      
    <p id="_c52252d9-191b-4edd-903f-4cc6a1b034d6">Managing information security risks related to people, process, technology and governance.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_d1e01c3c-02cf-4888-ab34-ce2f92100604">Oversight of the effective implementation of the technology controls.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_1771ff17-a476-490a-82bb-8037ee3a72d2">Oversight of risk management practices.</p>      
  </li>      
</ol>     
</specification>
<verification exclude="false">     
  <ol id="_d1a4197d-9791-4ea1-ba51-570bd200b98b" type="arabic">      
  <li>      
    <p id="_421bdec6-47f1-498e-8010-1807dd13336e">Determine that the responsibilities of management and board of directors in managing and overseeing information security risks are documented and communicated.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_e3780d51-a018-43ba-b207-369e814b205e">Inspect documents such as meeting minutes and committee charter to identify the participants involved in the meeting or committee, their respective job functions and the reporting relationship.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_657eb011-4459-4228-87d9-674314c8bbb1">Determine whether the management and board of directors meet regularly, at an appropriate and monitored frequency.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_373e78d4-b317-4587-bdac-b239531689c2">Determine whether the information security function is headed by a Chief Information Security Officer (CISO) or similar function.</p>      
  </li>      
</ol>     
</verification></requirement>   
</clause>  
<clause id="_level_2_requirements_and_audit_procedures" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">   
  <title>Level 2 requirements and audit procedures</title>   
  <requirement id="_af75d1c6-56f5-4ac5-b85d-d1cf1810d974"><label>/ss/584/2015/level/2</label><inherit>/ss/584/2015/level/1</inherit><description><p id="_80d86dc3-4a99-403f-a97f-1e209262e4fe">The requirements and audit procedures are the same as those in Level 1.</p>    
</description><verification exclude="false"/></requirement>   
</clause>  
<clause id="_level_3_requirements_and_audit_procedures" inline-header="false" obligation="normative"><title>Level 3 requirements and audit procedures</title><requirement id="_290821a2-e65e-4b20-afad-af38cd858c12"><label>/ss/584/2015/level/3</label><inherit>/ss/584/2015/level/2</inherit><description><p id="_2456c007-1831-4710-bb76-87f99194c952">The requirements are the same as those in Level 2.</p>    
</description><verification exclude="false"><p id="_2736c068-cc40-4432-bfa9-7d7cc9e5187b">The audit procedures are those in Level 1 and the following:</p>     
<ol id="_891a7954-d393-4f3c-9f1d-efc39de81f6e" type="arabic">      
  <li>      
    <p id="_7171ab4f-abe6-4671-8983-a7221abe6f23">Verify risks have been reviewed, understood, and addressed (i.e. including a cost benefit analysis) by management and the board.</p>      
  </li>      
</ol></verification></requirement>   
